text: Tootje Selbach (born 14 March 1928) is a retired Dutch gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Dutch female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
